  [Text] Stepanakert ("Azg" daily), 03/03/94 -- The RMK 
[Republic of Mountainous Karabakh] Ministry of Foreign Affairs 
reports, the legislative bodies in the republic destroyed 
107,710 sq.m. of narcotics plantations. 8,619 grams of drugs 
