providing support. It was just to exchange opinions. 
  Unidentified reporter: Mr. Prosecutor, one last 
question. It would seem that your WASHINGTON POST article has 
caused quite a frenzy in the United States. 
  De Greiff: That is correct. I am very sorry that 
this has been the case. It would seem that the Americans are 
very thin-skinned. [end recording] 

