<F P=102>  PY2503020394 </F>
<F P=103> PY2503020394 </F>
<F P=104></F>



<TEXT>
Article   Type:BFN 

  [Editorial Report] Rio de Janeiro JORNAL DO BRASIL in 
Portuguese on 2 March publishes on page 15 a 300-word 
unattributed article on the increasing consumption of "skunk," a 
more potent form of marijuana, in Rio de Janeiro. This article 
quotes Federal Police operations chief Roberto Frei as saying 
